{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d20fa993-f727-43d4-9752-b2571ee6f419", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20fa993-f727-43d4-9752-b2571ee6f419@1.pkg/1772597600763/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597601615", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20fa993-f727-43d4-9752-b2571ee6f419@1.pkg/1772597600763/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597601615"}, "identifier": "d20fa993-f727-43d4-9752-b2571ee6f419", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>③④:市民通过扫二维码就能进入数字政务大厅办理业务，累计服务超过500万人次，这创新了政务服务方式，使政府能够更快速、高效地为群众服务，故③④符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>①:这种便捷的政务服务方式，让政府服务更高效，不是对政府权力的监督，故①不符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>②:“数字政务服务门牌”举措并未增加行政机关数量，只是改变了政务服务的方式，故②说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025四川成都中考真题）某市首创“数字政务服务门牌”，市民只需要扫一扫家门口的二维码，就能进入数字政务大厅办理相关亦务。截至2024年底，“数字政务服务门牌”已接入二维码户室牌472.82万个，累计服务超过500万人次。该举措（&nbsp; &nbsp; ）</p>\n\n<p>①杜绝了政府权力滥用 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>②增加了行政机关数量</p>\n\n<p>③创新了政务服务方式&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>④增强了群众的获得感</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025四川成都中考真题）某市首创“数字政务服务门牌”，市民只需要扫一扫家门口的二维码，就能进入数字政务大厅办理相关亦务。截至2024年底，“数字政务服务门牌”已接入二维码户室牌472.82万个，累计服务超过500万人次。该举措（    ）①杜绝了政府权力滥用                          ②增加了行政机关数量③创新了政务服务方式                    ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20fa993-f727-43d4-9752-b2571ee6f419@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754818677185", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2025四川成都中考真题）某市首创“数字政务服务门牌”，市民只需要扫一扫家门口的二维码，就能进入数字政务大厅办理相关亦务。截至2024年底，“数字政务服务门牌”已接入二维码户室牌472.82万个，累计服务超过500万人次。该举措（&nbsp; &nbsp; ）</p>\n\n<p>①杜绝了政府权力滥用 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>②增加了行政机关数量</p>\n\n<p>③创新了政务服务方式&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>④增强了群众的获得感</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-librar